ai_analysis.summary: Many users are discussing their experience and expectations with Sodex, while also sharing their knowledge and asking questions about the project, including its potential for financial freedom and the possibility of receiving rewards. There is a sense of community and camaraderie, with users supporting and encouraging one another. Some users are inquiring about the SosoValue exp and roles, as well as the requirements to get the Sodex user role. Others are asking about the relationship between Sodex and SosoValue, and how to get more roles. There is also a discussion about the importance of staying safe and avoiding scams.
questions: What are the requirements to get the Sodex user role?
How can users get more roles in Sodex and SosoValue?
